thread.title: Valued Customer Sheila
thread.title_full: EasyKeys.com reviewed by Valued Customer Sheila

author: Valued Customer Sheila
title: Valued Customer Sheila
text: I needed keys for an old file cabinet in my office. It was nice being able to locate the brand/key number so quickly. The only reason for 4 stars is because I had a coupon code and could not find the place to use it during the checkout process. It's not as simple as with other sites.
